            "text": " endpoint and integrate with tools like Prometheus for alerting. At Ben's 2 dollar shop, implementing caching for frequent queries reduced API calls by 40%. Ensure idempotency in POST requests by including unique IDs in payloads to prevent duplicate processing during retries."
